parts.text: Calendar Data: 2025-03-14 09:00 - 10:30 | Sprint Planning | Agenda: 1. Review last sprint 2. Define sprint goals To-do: Assign tasks by 2025-03-15.
Summary: Sprint Planning meeting from 9:00 to 10:30 AM on 2025-03-14 to review the previous sprint and define new goals. Tasks are to be assigned by 2025-03-15.
